00:19:26,449 --> 00:19:27,948
Kelihatannya kau belum paham juga.

225
00:19:31,189 --> 00:19:34,188
Omong-omong, bagaiamana istri dan putrimu...

226
00:19:34,459 --> 00:19:35,729
...di Amerika?

227
